               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18341016-84-person859">
                  EDMUND 
                  BRIEN
               <interp inst="t18341016-84-person859" type="surname" value="BRIEN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-84-person859" type="given" value="EDMUND"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18341016-84-person859" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I lodge at Mrs. Hanton's - I lost a pair of trowsers and a waistcoat on the <rs id="t18341016-84-cd471" type="crimeDate">4th of September</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-84-off466 t18341016-84-cd471"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18341016-84-off470 t18341016-84-cd471"></join> - I saw the trowsers at a beer-shop, where Shuffrey was wearing them - the waistcoat was at the pawnbroker's - I know nothing against Hanton.</p>
               <p>Shuffrey. Hanton gave me the trowsers to wear - the waistcoat was at my mother's, and Brien said I might pawn it. Witness. No, I did not.</p>
